{"tid":47692,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"招人拍片","createTime":"2016-12-20T13:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T07:11:25.000Z","uid":40094,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"727b149d813c5e0e24022d1bb1f906776d613f53","tid":47692,"uid":40094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:40:51.000Z","msg":"小弟想搵可以長期合作同肯出鏡既人拍片<br />\n男女皆可 20歲以上 對拍片無經驗都無問題 因為小弟都係略知一二 <br />\n拍片類型會偏向娛樂性質或者能夠帶出到正能量 <br />\n偏向無里頭幾分鐘左右甚至係幾秒類似Vine既片 <br />\n可以既話 最好除左星期六日 一至五都可以抽時間出黎或者拍片 <br />\n最緊要係有熱誠同埋係認真 <br />\n有意有心就pm電話 再傾下睇下夾唔夾到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n皆因我發現依度個PM功能仲未用到<br />\n所以麻煩大家inbox我新開既Facebook account<br />\n大家直接禁下面條link再inbox 我知係有啲麻煩 但真係有興趣 就inbox我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw 我試過直接search 個fb係搵唔到，所以禁下面條link, 個profile pic 係阿寶黎<br />\n<br />\nFb: 李訊息<br />\n<a href=\"http://zh-hk.facebook.com/people/%E6%9D%8E%E8%A8%8A%E6%81%AF/100014578634595\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh-hk.facebook.com%2Fpeople%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E8%25A8%258A%25E6%2581%25AF%2F100014578634595&d=Lrz33MO9%2FF%2BgA77gwrfowXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=ae1fb0cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">zh-hk.facebook.com/people/%E6%9D%8E%E8%A8%8A%E6%81%AF/100014578634595</a>"},{"pid":"05e501a267215ccc0b677c9c3a4b4905cfe8f2ed","tid":47692,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eceac78e254cb8959156069069d5177b12e3eba7","tid":47692,"uid":51512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:47:26.000Z","msg":"人工？"},{"pid":"bae53f77ccb8834d21417f199b3f574fe8e3cb0c","tid":47692,"uid":40094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T14:24:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人工？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大家一齊玩"},{"pid":"d027d5eaf7022bc8d90852b902cd9a4fd8aea966","tid":47692,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T14:50:08.000Z","msg":"巴打講唔講下自己少少資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a06d7eba0ae57da255c738bdfb153dc78791f0b","tid":47692,"uid":40094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T18:49:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打講唔講下自己少少資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實已經搞左一段時間 但因為人手時間問題 真係唔係好夾到 搞到好難run 所以先想搵多啲有共同方向一齊搞"},{"pid":"388828cf4f4260845f5111774a9064834b40f74b","tid":47692,"uid":26324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T19:13:05.000Z","msg":"我一直都想拍。樣子正常。觀塘附近我okay。"},{"pid":"796eb652802e939b3b5843dcd1256f54b71767e5","tid":47692,"uid":40094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T19:47:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我一直都想拍。樣子正常。觀塘附近我okay。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係要係觀塘附近meeting or 拍片？"},{"pid":"9d78f7aaf0025ce06ef43c43fa965e83c24c5429","tid":47692,"uid":2746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T20:06:47.000Z","msg":"唔好太早，亦唔好太夜<br />\n太柒唔拍，太on9唔拍，太正經都唔怕<br />\n最好有囡<br />\n要經我同意先可以upload<br />\n拍得我太醜怪唔俾up<br />\n青衣附近，包食飯"},{"pid":"8a778941ab0109ea6a9ebe48b8fc5aaa2db42250","tid":47692,"uid":40094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T04:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65d324b884a52927fd1066604ec5f28cf0ffebb","tid":47692,"uid":61049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T04:34:05.000Z","msg":"毒撚是不適合上鏡的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af38ab7bc5291756505d23cffeb063fe5b6a6556","tid":47692,"uid":26324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re